Program: Discovery
Title: Three deadly diseases
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrx8s
Last Broadcast Date: 11 December 1998
A report on three illnesses which could pose a threat to us all in the new millennium. A new strain of bubonic plague has raised concern over a new 'black death'. The programme also includes a report on HIV and Aids and Alzheimer's disease.